  <h1>Chapel Hill Therapy in a Comfortable Setting</h1>
  <p>
  Thank you for visiting my site.  My name is Holly FitzGerald, and I am a Licensed Clinical Social Worker (<acronym title="Licensed Clinical Social Worker">LCSW</acronym>). I expect you are here because you are looking for a therapist for yourself or a loved one.
  </p>
  <p>
  As a Clinical Social Worker, I have been in private practice in Chapel Hill since 1989, and worked with various social service agencies since 1971.  I have worked with, and continue to work with a broad range of populations, from children to the aging.  I work with individuals, couples and families, of any orientation and combination.  Help with childhood difficulties, pre-marital counseling, end of life counseling and help with life changes along the way are all part of my expertise.
  </p>
  <cfset indeximage = "indeximage" & randRange(1,3) />
